'Hierarchical Permalinks'=>'分层永久链接','Default'=>'默认','Select Color'=>'选择颜色','Current Color'=>'当前颜色','1.x Updates'=>'1.x 更新','<h3>Menu Label</h3> This is the label that will appear throughout the WordPress admin area for your settings.'=>'<h3>菜单标签</h3> 这是整个WordPress设置管理区域中显示的标签。','<h3>Menu Location</h3> This is the location where the new settings page will be added in the WordPress Dashboard menu.'=>'<h3>菜单位置</h3> 此处是在WordPress仪表板菜单中添加新设置页面的位置。','<h3>Page Title</h3> This is the text that will appear at the top of your settings page.'=>'<h3>页面标题</h3> 此处将显示设置页面顶部的文本。','<h3>Plural Label</h3> This is the label for more than 1 item (Plural) that will appear throughout the WordPress admin area for managing the content.'=>'<h3复数标签</h3>这是多个项目（多个）的标签，将出现在整个WordPress管理区域中，用于管理内容。','<h3>Pod Identifier</h3> This is different than the labels users will see in the WordPress admin areas, it is the name you will use to programatically reference this object throughout your theme, WordPress, and other PHP.'=>'<h3>Pod 标识</h3>这不同于用户在WordPress管理区域中看到的标签，它是您将在整个主题、WordPress和其他PHP中以编程方式引用此对象的名称。','<h3>Post Types</h3> WordPress can hold and display many different types of content. Internally, these are all stored in the same place, in the wp_posts table. These are differentiated by a column called post_type.'=>'<h3>内容类型</h3> WordPress 可以保存和显示许多不同类型的内容。在内部，这些都存储在相同的位置，即wp_posts表中。它们用一个名为post_type的列来区分。','<h3>Singular Label</h3> This is the label for 1 item (Singular) that will appear throughout the WordPress admin area for managing the content.'=>'<h3>单数标签</h3>这是一个项目的标签（单数），将出现在整个WordPress管理区域中，用于管理内容。','<h3>Storage Types</h3> Table based storage will operate in a way where each field you create for your content type becomes a field in a table. Meta based storage relies upon the WordPress meta storage table for all field data.'=>'<h3>存储类型</h3>基于表的存储将以下方式运行，即您为内容类型创建的每个字段都将成为表中的一个字段。基于元的存储依赖于WordPress存放所有字段数据的元存储表。','<h3>Taxonomies</h3> A taxonomy is a way to group Post Types.'=>'<h3>分类法</h3>分类法是对内容类型进行分组的一种方法。','After Content'=>'内容之后','Before Content'=>'内容之前','Bi-directional Field'=>'双向传输字段','Bi-directional fields will update their related field for any item you select. This feature is only available for two relationships between two Pods.<br /><br />For example, when you update a Parent pod item to relate to a Child item, when you go to edit that Child item you will see the Parent pod item selected.'=>'相关联的字段将在你选择任意一项时更新相关字段，此特性只在两个相关联的Pods之间可用<br /><br />。例如：当你更新一个父Pods到一个相关的子Pods，当你编辑子条目时，你会发现父Pod也被选中了。','Choose a Pod'=>'选择一个 Pod','Custom Query Var Name'=>'自定义查询变量名称','Detail Page URL'=>'详情页面网址','Display a field from this item'=>'显示此项目中的字段','Due to a number of optimizations in Pods 2.x, we need to run a few updates to your database. This should not remove or change your existing Pod data from 1.x, so if you wish to rollback to Pods 1.x - you can easily do that.'=>'由于Pods 2.x中的许多优化，我们需要对你的数据库运行一些更新。这不会从1.x中删除或更改您现有的Pod数据，因此如果您希望回滚到Pod 1.x - 您可以轻松地做到这一点。','During this process your Pods, Settings, and Content will be migrated into the optimized Pods 2.x architecture. We will not delete any of your old data, the tables will remain until you choose to clean them up after a successful upgrade.'=>'处理过程中，你的 Pods、设置和内容将被迁移到优化过的 Pods2.0 中，我们不会删除您的任何旧数据，直到您选择在成功升级后清理它们之前这些表将一直保留。','Function to call when updating counts'=>'更新计数时要调用的函数','Genesis: Simple Sidebars'=>'通用：简易侧边栏','https://pods.io/'=>'https://pods.io/','https://pods.io/about/'=>'https://pods.io/about/','If you delete the "name" field, we need to specify the field to use as your primary title field. This field will serve as an index of your content. Most commonly this field represents the name of a person, place, thing, or a summary field.'=>'如果删除了 "名称" 字段，我们需要指定要用作主要标题字段的字段。通常此字段内容为人名、地点、事物或概括性描述。','Item Indexes'=>'项目索引','Jetpack Markdown Support'=>'Jetpack Markdown 支持','Jetpack Publicize Support'=>'Jetpack Publicize 支持','Menu Label'=>'菜单标签','Meta Based (WP Default)'=>'基于元数据（WP 默认）','Migrating Your Cont